caption.p: Volcano plots of all proteins identified and quantified, illustrating their magnitude, significance, and direction of differential expression observed after 24 h exposure to CNTs (SWCNT, MWCNT) at two different concentrations, 10 Î¼g/mL, 100 ng/mL.
